  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate the Clinical performance of the near-infrared imaging
      system VistaCam iX Proxi in comparison with digital radiographic findings and ICDAS-II in
      detection of approximal carious lesions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
